  "short_description": "Battle it out with hiragana in this dungeon crawler RPG designed to teach you to read Japanese. Utilizing a full professional music track and a fully voiced script to immerse you in the game, along with RPG elements and well-paced learning, you’ll master hiragana before you know it.",
