  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/b0417300b85f6f910c04409458f4b324.poster.avif?t=1764670113\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/b0417300b85f6f910c04409458f4b324.webm?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/b0417300b85f6f910c04409458f4b324.mp4?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to read, recognize, and use <i>hiragana </i>as you are guided by Keen Reflex through a 35-floor ever-changing labyrinth in an addictive and educational dungeon crawler RPG! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learning to read <i>hiragana </i>is the first step in your Japanese learning journey and the first hurdle that learners struggle to overcome.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This addictive RPG dungeon crawler will have you reading Japanese in record time without all that boring study.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles to seek out the hiragana monsters and make your way through the labyrinth to the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/049ae80dc622355520893f6119651547.poster.avif?t=1764670113\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/049ae80dc622355520893f6119651547.webm?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/049ae80dc622355520893f6119651547.mp4?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle Hiragana</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the correct reading of the hiragana to defeat the monsters and gain experience. Make too many mistakes and it's back to the beginning! Don't worry, though. You'll keep your levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/774e8c86044596d1d3816195d37778af.poster.avif?t=1764670113\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/774e8c86044596d1d3816195d37778af.webm?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/774e8c86044596d1d3816195d37778af.mp4?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Flashcards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your newfound knowledge of hiragana to correctly read and obtain flashcards. Collect all 50 to greatly increase your rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/920dac6c5006479dac776df77c6427c3.poster.avif?t=1764670113\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/920dac6c5006479dac776df77c6427c3.webm?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/920dac6c5006479dac776df77c6427c3.mp4?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Raise Stats Through Levels and Gear</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just knowing the hiragana won't be enough to defeat the hordes of hiragana. You'll have to raise your stats by leveling up and buying stronger equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/806bd1b16b5e49fe2f7b724bea871b70.poster.avif?t=1764670113\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/806bd1b16b5e49fe2f7b724bea871b70.webm?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/806bd1b16b5e49fe2f7b724bea871b70.mp4?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/b0417300b85f6f910c04409458f4b324.poster.avif?t=1764670113\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/b0417300b85f6f910c04409458f4b324.webm?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/b0417300b85f6f910c04409458f4b324.mp4?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to read, recognize, and use <i>hiragana </i>as you are guided by Keen Reflex through a 35-floor ever-changing labyrinth in an addictive and educational dungeon crawler RPG! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learning to read <i>hiragana </i>is the first step in your Japanese learning journey and the first hurdle that learners struggle to overcome.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This addictive RPG dungeon crawler will have you reading Japanese in record time without all that boring study.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles to seek out the hiragana monsters and make your way through the labyrinth to the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/049ae80dc622355520893f6119651547.poster.avif?t=1764670113\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/049ae80dc622355520893f6119651547.webm?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/049ae80dc622355520893f6119651547.mp4?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle Hiragana</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the correct reading of the hiragana to defeat the monsters and gain experience. Make too many mistakes and it's back to the beginning! Don't worry, though. You'll keep your levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/774e8c86044596d1d3816195d37778af.poster.avif?t=1764670113\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/774e8c86044596d1d3816195d37778af.webm?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/774e8c86044596d1d3816195d37778af.mp4?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Flashcards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your newfound knowledge of hiragana to correctly read and obtain flashcards. Collect all 50 to greatly increase your rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/920dac6c5006479dac776df77c6427c3.poster.avif?t=1764670113\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/920dac6c5006479dac776df77c6427c3.webm?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/920dac6c5006479dac776df77c6427c3.mp4?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Raise Stats Through Levels and Gear</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just knowing the hiragana won't be enough to defeat the hordes of hiragana. You'll have to raise your stats by leveling up and buying stronger equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/806bd1b16b5e49fe2f7b724bea871b70.poster.avif?t=1764670113\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/806bd1b16b5e49fe2f7b724bea871b70.webm?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019360/extras/806bd1b16b5e49fe2f7b724bea871b70.mp4?t=1764670113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
